\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af1\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af1\langfe2052\hich\f1\fs24\lang2057\loch\f1\fs24\lang2057 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057\i0\b0 \tab Death of a Friend follows me, every time I leave the building; I never see her door open, and I am wary, for Mr. Lights, her father, most definitely hates me; no one else has fallen under his spell, but I hear him shouting about me from his room, and the 
