\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af1\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af1\langfe2052\hich\f1\fs24\lang2057\loch\f1\fs24\lang2057 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057\i0\b0 \tab Today, though, she came to my door, and offered to show me more of the town. I had yet to explore much deeper than the main thoroughfare and the channels and bridges surrounding the water and my apartment. I agreed; her dress was short and I was sick of w
