\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af1\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af1\langfe2052\hich\f1\fs24\lang2057\loch\f1\fs24\lang2057 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057\i0\b0 \tab We mounted the steps to a vast rotunda, again portal-less, decorated with statues of vast men and beasts, all of them being tortured by vile devices or projections. Both Friend and I searched for any crevice or depression that might give a way an opening,
