r his back and constantly dripping steam from his panting breath. There were scratches in the paper beside the drawing.\tab }
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af1\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af1\langfe2052\hich\f1\fs24\lang2057\loch\f1\fs24\lang2057 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057\i0\b0 \tab The small sphere tied at the waist waist is called the Cerebellum Clandestin, and seems the most important part of the game. Within is contained, on a spiralling, microfilmic canvas, the entire life story of the player, in excruciating detail, down to the
