\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af1\afs24\lang1081\ltrch\dbch\af1\langfe2052\hich\f1\fs24\lang2057\loch\f1\fs24\lang2057 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f8\fs24\lang2057\i0\b0 \tab I went down the River Walk to try and escape the grain in the air. It is an old street, bordered by high, dry-stone walls and climbing ivy, snow-blossom and petunias, peppered with gateways leading to mansions and the observatories of the rich. Before I r
